}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "LPCY0063 REV:1.2" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. The chip is not identifiable in the FCC photos.
Based on this device's specifications, it's presumed to be using RTL8814AU. :It's a [[Realtek]] chipset device based on the included driver set. :The USB ID would be expected to be [http://usb-ids.gowdy.us/read/UD/20f4/809b 20f4:809b].
